  <h1>Travel</h1>

  <p class="intro large">The whole day will take place at Kirknewton House Stables, in the village of Kirknewton to the west of Edinburgh.</p>

  <p class="intro">The wedding service will start at 2.20pm, we suggest you aim to arrive around 2.00pm.  If you are coming for the evening only, please try to arrive at 8.00pm.  The evening will finish around 11.30pm.</p>


