  <div class="box box-directions">
    <h2>By Car</h2>
    <p class="first">There is some parking at the Stables if you plan on driving.  The postcode for your satnav is <strong>EH27 8DA</strong></p>
    <p>When you turn down the drive to Kirknewton House, follow the sign for the Stables, and then you will see a sign for parking on the right. The stables are a short walk from the car park.</p>
