  <div class="box box-directions">
    <h2>Getting Home</h2>
    <p class="first">If you’re going home via public transport, there are trains throughout the evening leaving from Kirknewton train station travelling back into Edinburgh City Centre. The last two leave at <strong>22:21</strong>, and <strong>00:09</strong>.  If you plan on catching the last train, please feel free to help us with some tidying up before you go!</p>

    <p>You can also get the number <strong>28</strong> bus from Kirknewton village, which leaves from Main Street, outside a pub (the Kirknewton Inn), near the post office.  That’s a 10 minute walk from the Stables.  It leaves at 5 minutes past the hour, the last bus is at <strong>23:05</strong>.  <a href="http://www.firstgroup.com/ukbus/scotland_east/journey_planning/timetables/timetable.php?day=2&source_id=2&service=27/28/X27/X28&routeid=9195151&operator=25&source=sp" target="_blank">View the full timetable</a>.</p>

